                "imgDesc": "<p>This tower contains highly specialized active machines and Eliphas Beam Emitters. The roofs of some floors will contain <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">beam-emitting assemblies</span> that you can <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">turn </span>using the corresponding mechanical valves.</p>",
