              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/04/35428890/a6492bc8854b6f7560e74cfc670cdadc_1514324995104958143.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The matching item to this is a specially designed beam receptor. As the name suggests, it will only be activated after it <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">absorbs a beam</span>.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/04/35428890/1971962abd6c20e2f2203af95f8976f9_3891343630126556203.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The wheeled assembly carrying the custom beam emitter can use mechanical means to adjust its <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">horizontal position.</span></p>",
